# Project Documentation

## Project Title

Voice-Based Concept Understanding Analyzer (VBCUA)

## Description

The Voice-Based Concept Understanding Analyzer is an AI-powered educational application that evaluates students' conceptual understanding from spoken explanations. It converts speech into text, compares it with reference answers using semantic similarity analysis, generates scores, provides feedback, and creates downloadable PDF reports.

## Technologies Used

- Python
- Streamlit
- OpenAI Whisper
- Sentence Transformers
- ReportLab
- Librosa

